{"tid":2222282,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「懲教黑幕」監獄搶錢家族 霸佔訪客處賣探監用品圖利 活躍兩年月賺10萬","createTime":"2020-09-29T04:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T04:03:34.000Z","uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ad275be486ad4fea7cefef06cc9e2d70470144c5","tid":2222282,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9Hgc4-odvzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9Hgc4-odvzU&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=454ed883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9Hgc4-odvzU</a><br />\n<br />\n監獄搶錢家族 霸佔訪客處賣探監用品圖利 活躍兩年月賺10萬<br />\n<br />\n荔枝角收押所的訪客登記處，本是讓在囚人士的親友辦理探監手續的場所，可是，有讀者向我們報料指，每天都有一個家庭式集團在這裏販賣探監物品，更離譜的是，他們霸佔了多個原本供探監人士擺放私人物品的儲物櫃作存貨之用；不過，在場的保安人員卻一直未有阻止他們的行為。除了賣探監物品，這一家人也提供代客探監的服務，亦染指赤柱監獄的相關生意。消息指，這個監獄搶錢家族每月賺取的利潤超過十萬，相當可觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/skipped-hk/20200904/S7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fskipped-hk%2F20200904%2FS7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=a82861b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fskipped-hk%2F20200904%2FS7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI%2F&h=bbe4f63c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/skipped-hk/20200904/S7MOF3QGFJOXS4QGOSF5QBKJEI/</a>"},{"pid":"5c3004c5d48b06cd6e24d1e3ac6316c3510491c3","tid":2222282,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce316f0537fdf5763a50399069d7039ccca7c5f","tid":2222282,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"在荔枝角收押所外專營探訪日用品的士多負責人，一早知道蓮姐的存在，直斥<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>其行為非法，並質疑她有甚麼人給她撐腰</strong></span></span>。由於這個監獄搶錢家族，在荔枝角收押所活躍兩年，但卻一直未被懲教職員干預，因此，引起很多人不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港已經同大陸正式接軌！<br />\n只要屋企人係有權勢人士 日日犯法都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775c82612c249a1285ff5a8f3b71c2bf31a987c7","tid":2222282,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e927def01566b42f5c073541c41f8392b86d1927","tid":2222282,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"點止啊 醫院食環 都好多搞葬禮嘅搵食"}]}